      <title>秘鲁顶级银行家将就向政治家子弟提供现金捐赠表态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/credicorp-s-former-chairman-to-take-stand-in-peru-trial-against-keiko-fujimori</link>
