    <item>
      <title>法国大选博弈中勒庞的权力之路愈发狭窄</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/le-pen-s-path-to-power-narrows-in-french-game-of-election-chess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在竞争对手采取措施减少三方竞选的数量以减少在立法选举的最后一轮中有利于玛丽娜·勒庞的极右翼政党获胜之后，玛丽娜·勒庞所领导的国民联盟在组建法国下一届政府时面临着更大的障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/le-pen-s-path-to-power-narrows-in-french-game-of-election-chess</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:56:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱在访问巴西前称卢拉是“白痴恐龙”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/milei-calls-lula-an-idiot-dinosaur-ahead-of-brazil-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱称路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦是“愚蠢的恐龙”和共产主义者，这进一步加剧了阿根廷与邻国之间的长期不和。而就在前一天，米莱还选择在卢拉即将访问巴西时拒绝他的到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/milei-calls-lula-an-idiot-dinosaur-ahead-of-brazil-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲁迪·朱利安尼因 2020 年为特朗普工作而失去纽约律师执照</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/rudy-giuliani-loses-his-new-york-law-license-for-trump-2020-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鲁道夫·朱利安尼因协助唐纳德·特朗普推翻 2020 年总统大选结果而被吊销了纽约律师执照，这是对这位曾经备受赞誉的联邦检察官和纽约市长的最新打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/rudy-giuliani-loses-his-new-york-law-license-for-trump-2020-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:40:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞或将在极右翼改组中放弃其所属的欧洲议会党团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/le-pen-may-ditch-her-eu-parliament-group-in-far-right-shakeup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞领导的运动的官员正在与欧洲议会的其他极右翼团体进行深入谈判，这可能会导致她的政党放弃现有的政治家族，与匈牙利的维克托·奥尔班联手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/le-pen-may-ditch-her-eu-parliament-group-in-far-right-shakeup</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:40:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
