      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:25:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将会见民主党州长，力图拉近关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-to-meet-democratic-governors-as-he-looks-to-close-ranks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登计划与民主党州长进行会谈，同时他正努力平息要求结束其连任竞选并让另一位候选人与唐纳德·特朗普竞争的呼声。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-to-meet-democratic-governors-as-he-looks-to-close-ranks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:25:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉与美国将在总统选举前恢复谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/venezuela-us-to-resume-talks-ahead-of-presidential-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗表示，委内瑞拉政府将在 7 月 28 日总统大选之前于本月与拜登政府恢复谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/venezuela-us-to-resume-talks-ahead-of-presidential-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 02:48:04 GMT</pubDate>
